Interface ListMap<K,V>

    public interface ListMap<K,V>
extends CollectionMap<K,List<V>,V>

    int index)
        Returns the value at the specified index in the list mapped to the specified key.

        key - the key of the list to get the value from

          V value)

        Parameters:
        key - the key of the list to return the index from
        value - the value of the list to return the index of
        Returns:
